data.description: Price reduced ! Welcome to the lowest priced detached home in all of Timonium ! And we just completed a full on rehab throughout. Conveniently located just one block off of York Road and  situated on a deep, fenced wooded lot      with a huge shed and off street paved parking for 4 cars ! That's right, and did I mention that price? ! Three finished floors with brand new kitchen and appliances and fully restored original hardwoods throughout. This one is move in ready on a CLEAN &  tidy street with pride of ownership throughout ! There's also a rear deck on which to view your private spacious yard. Come check it out this weekend!  Seller requests Gemini Title & Escrow, LLC. Ground rent to be determined by buyer, seller will not redeem.
